channel.title: CVE Feed for Hitachi -- RAID Manager Storage Replication Adapter
channel.description: The latest CVEs for Hitachi -- RAID Manager Storage Replication Adapter

item.title: CVE-2022-34882|2024-08-03T09:22:10.618Z -- hitachi -- raid%20manager%20storage%20replication%20adapter
item.description: Information Exposure Through an Error Message vulnerability in Hitachi RAID Manager Storage Replication Adapter allows remote authenticated users to gain sensitive information. This issue affects: Hitachi RAID Manager Storage Replication Adapter 02.01.04 versions prior to 02.03.02 on Windows; 02.05.00 versions prior to 02.05.01 on Windows and Docker.

item.title: CVE-2022-34883|2024-08-03T09:22:10.705Z -- hitachi -- raid%20manager%20storage%20replication%20adapter
item.description: OS Command Injection vulnerability in Hitachi RAID Manager Storage Replication Adapter allows remote authenticated users to execute arbitrary OS commands. This issue affects: Hitachi RAID Manager Storage Replication Adapter 02.01.04 versions prior to 02.03.02 on Windows; 02.05.00 versions prior to 02.05.01 on Windows and Docker.
